## Simulation Commands

Always be able to run simulation with:
  ./scripts/simulate.sh cpu      # Simulates CPU with directed tests
  ./scripts/simulate.sh accel    # Simulates accelerator standalone
  ./scripts/simulate.sh uvm      # Runs full UVM regression
  ./scripts/simulate.sh formal   # Runs SymbiYosys on both targets

Each command should exit 0 on pass, non-zero on any failure.
Test pass/fail must be printed clearly to stdout.

